### Variables
@baseUrl = https://stock-sentinel-9wq1.onrender.com 
## http://localhost:8080
@symbol = AMAT

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create a Position
POST {{baseUrl}}/positions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "AMAT",
  "entry_price": 529.66,
  "quantity": 10
}

### Get All Positions
GET {{baseUrl}}/positions

### Get Fast Signal
# Technical rules only. High frequency polling.
GET {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{symbol}}/signal

### Get Full Signal
# Slow: Technical + News + LLM analysis. Poll every 15-30 minutes.
GET {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{symbol}}/full-signal

### Evaluate Candidates
# Screen potential buys
POST {{baseUrl}}/candidates/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbols": ["NVDA", "AMD", "MSFT"]
}

### Delete a Position
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/positions/{{symbol}}